 ## Current Notes
-- Add or refresh notes here.
+- Last refreshed: 2026-03-05 (Phase 0 - Refresh Atlas Context)
+
+## Project Purpose
+- Frontend for Huz web booking experience: discovery, package details, booking flow, and authenticated user self-service pages.
+- Stack: React 18 + `react-scripts` (CRA), React Router v6, Tailwind CSS, Axios, Context API.
+
+## High-Level Architecture
+- Bootstrap: `src/index.js` mounts `src/App.js`.
+- App shell (`src/App.js`) composes providers and routing:
+  - `AuthContextProvider`
+  - `CurrencyProvider`
+  - `ModalProvider`
+  - `BookingProvider`
+  - `BrowserRouter` + `AppRoutes`
+- Route layer (`src/routes/AppRoutes.jsx`) lazy-loads page modules and wraps private routes with `ProtectedRoute`.
+- Data layer:
+  - Core HTTP client + token lifecycle in `src/services/api/httpClient.js`.
+  - Domain API wrappers in `src/api/*` (`AuthApi`, `apiService`, `homepageApi`, `listingApi`, legacy `UserAuthApis`).
+
+## Critical Flows
+1. Visitor discovery flow
+- Home (`/`) -> listing (`/listing-page`) via query params (`type`, `departureLocation`, `departureDate`) -> package detail (`/package-detail-page?PackageId=...`).
+- Home and listing data come from `src/api/homepageApi.js` and `src/api/listingApi.js`.
+
+2. Auth and session flow
+- Login/signup/otp routes use `src/api/AuthApi.js`.
+- Auth tokens are persisted in cookies (`accessToken`, `refreshToken`) and refreshed through `/api/token/refresh/` interceptor logic in `httpClient`.
+- `ProtectedRoute` blocks private routes and renders login prompt when unauthenticated.
+
+3. Booking and post-booking flow
+- Package detail booking widgets call booking endpoints through `src/api/apiService.js` (`/booking/new/create/` and related booking-number endpoints).
+- User settings pages use protected routes for bookings, payment methods, wallet, remaining payment, messages, and wishlist.
+
+## Scoped Area For Current Deep Scan Run
+- Run target project: `/Users/macbook/Desktop/Huz/Huz-Web-Frontend`.
+- Effective code scope for analysis phases: frontend source under `src/` plus supporting config in project root.
+- Orchestration run scope in state is `/Users/macbook/Desktop/Huz`; for this run, Phase 0 context was validated specifically against `Huz-Web-Frontend`.
